WEBVTT

00:00:00.006 --> 00:01:00.006

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
Episode 07

00:01:33.400 --> 00:01:35.200
Qian taught me something today.

00:01:35.920 --> 00:01:37.240
I wanna give it a shot.

00:01:37.560 --> 00:01:38.160
Wanzhi!

00:01:38.320 --> 00:01:38.880
See?

00:01:38.920 --> 00:01:40.280
I told you she's got guts.

00:01:40.800 --> 00:01:42.120
But we need equipment.

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:42.720
Right.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.200
We can rent a mic and speakers.

00:01:45.400 --> 00:01:46.960
Then we look like pros.

00:01:47.320 --> 00:01:48.790
Only pay ten yuan

00:01:48.800 --> 00:01:49.360
for a song.

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:50.480
They wouldn't say no.

00:01:50.680 --> 00:01:51.760
Smart investment

00:01:51.960 --> 00:01:53.360
leads to better returns.

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.320
That's a strategy.

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:57.480
You two are quite the duo.

00:01:58.880 --> 00:01:59.680
Not just Qian.

00:01:59.880 --> 00:02:01.200
Li Juan, you sing too.

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:03.040
Your styles are different.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:04.400
No way.

00:02:04.640 --> 00:02:05.240
Why not?

00:02:05.440 --> 00:02:07.000
You hum so nicely.

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:08.200
And your voice is loud.

00:02:08.440 --> 00:02:09.440
You can do it!

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:10.560
Yeah.

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:11.560
Though you're not

00:02:11.600 --> 00:02:13.360
as professional as me,

00:02:13.560 --> 00:02:14.950
many workers

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:15.960
love your style.

00:02:16.080 --> 00:02:17.160
Workers' friend.

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:18.200
We should

00:02:18.320 --> 00:02:20.440
pick outfits to match your styles.

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:21.680
That colorful dress

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:22.830
you bought the other day

00:02:22.840 --> 00:02:23.840
looks great on you.

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:24.600
Qian,

00:02:24.880 --> 00:02:25.880
keep this hairstyle.

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.070
The first time I saw you,

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:28.240
you looked like a star.

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:29.640
Really?

00:02:30.600 --> 00:02:31.600
And you?

00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:33.800
I can't sing.

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:36.160
I'll handle song requests
and collect the money.

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:37.680
We'll split the profits after.

00:02:38.240 --> 00:02:39.280
I'll take 20%.

00:02:39.440 --> 00:02:40.590
You two each get 40%.

00:02:40.600 --> 00:02:41.600
No.

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:43.080
If we're doing this together,

00:02:43.200 --> 00:02:44.200
we split it 50-50.

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:44.920
Exactly.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:45.520
Fifty-fifty.

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:46.480
Plus,

00:02:46.680 --> 00:02:48.080
help us with the song list.

00:02:48.600 --> 00:02:49.760
Most importantly,

00:02:50.080 --> 00:02:53.640
use your signature move.

00:02:54.960 --> 00:02:55.960
What move?

00:02:56.400 --> 00:02:57.480
Smiling.

00:02:58.080 --> 00:02:59.640
You have the sweetest smile.

00:02:59.760 --> 00:03:00.480
Your line

00:03:00.520 --> 00:03:01.880
is always packed with workers.

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:03.920
When they come to request a song,

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:05.880
flash them that smile.

00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:06.720
Then they will

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:07.840
request more.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:11.920
Yeah, exactly like that!

00:03:12.600 --> 00:03:13.720
Men love it.

00:03:14.640 --> 00:03:16.880
I love it even more!

00:03:17.160 --> 00:03:18.600
You're a man?

00:03:19.880 --> 00:03:20.880
Oh, come on.

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:22.560
No renting.

00:03:22.760 --> 00:03:23.760
Buy it

00:03:23.880 --> 00:03:24.880
or forget it.

00:03:26.320 --> 00:03:27.520
We can afford it.

00:03:27.960 --> 00:03:29.270
But we only need it for two days.

00:03:29.280 --> 00:03:30.280
Buying would be wasteful.

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:35.080
This is brand new.

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:36.560
If I rent it out,

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:38.280
who'll buy it then?

00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:39.720
Think about

00:03:39.760 --> 00:03:40.840
others, okay?

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:42.720
Handsome,

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:44.400
let's talk it over.

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:46.760
No is no.

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:50.000
Just lend it to us for two days.

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:51.720
We'll return it

00:03:51.800 --> 00:03:53.040
good as new.

00:04:02.440 --> 00:04:03.240
Giving my husband

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:04.520
the eye, huh?

00:04:05.000 --> 00:04:06.000
What do you want to do?

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:07.960
Get out!

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:16.000
Maybe we should forget it, Wanzhi.

00:04:16.080 --> 00:04:16.520
Just hit

00:04:16.520 --> 00:04:17.760
Window of the World

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:19.200
and snap a few photos.

00:04:19.640 --> 00:04:20.680
Keep hunting.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.120
This is the fifth one.

00:04:23.640 --> 00:04:25.320
If you give up too easily,

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:26.600
you'll never succeed.

00:04:27.640 --> 00:04:28.640
Fine!

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:29.600
Why don't we

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:31.480
go further out and look?

00:04:31.960 --> 00:04:33.400
Let's take a bus out of town.

00:04:33.840 --> 00:04:34.400
Good idea.

00:04:34.840 --> 00:04:35.840
Go.

00:04:37.040 --> 00:04:38.520
(Academy of Continuing Education)

00:04:38.600 --> 00:04:39.600
(welcomes you!)

00:04:39.760 --> 00:04:40.600
(Five associate's.)

00:04:40.600 --> 00:04:42.120
Evening classes and full-time study.

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:43.400
Self-study or correspondence.

00:04:46.320 --> 00:04:46.840
No need?

00:04:46.840 --> 00:04:47.870
(Welcome to)

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:48.640
(our school.)

00:04:48.640 --> 00:04:48.960
He...

00:04:49.240 --> 00:04:50.240
Where you going?

00:04:50.440 --> 00:04:51.000
Let's detour.

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:52.640
Why? Don't you see it?

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:53.200
Speakers!

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:53.720
What...

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:55.910
Yes. Speakers.

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:57.240
(Welcome to)

00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:57.880
(our school.)

00:04:58.400 --> 00:04:59.400
You know him, right?

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:01.160
Go!

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:02.920
Come on!

00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:06.600
(Academy of Continuing Education)

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:07.720
(welcomes you!)

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:09.120
(Five associate's, )

00:05:09.360 --> 00:05:10.560
(three bachelor's.)

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:12.720
(Lowest tuition in Shenzhen.)

00:05:14.720 --> 00:05:16.120
(Academy of Continuing Education)

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:17.280
(welcomes you!)

00:05:17.440 --> 00:05:18.680
(Five associate's.)

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:20.000
Fang Wanzhi!

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:22.280
What a coincidence!

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:24.280
Thanks for yesterday.

00:05:26.200 --> 00:05:27.680
If you really wanna thank me,

00:05:27.960 --> 00:05:28.960
sign up.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.390
I haven't hit

00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:31.400
my quota.

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:33.320
What's

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:33.960
with you?

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:35.120
It's too harsh.

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:37.160
Can this play backing tracks?

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:39.240
Of course.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:40.520
We use this

00:05:40.520 --> 00:05:41.200
for school shows.

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:42.760
I wanna rent this.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:44.560
Night use only. Won't affect your work.

00:05:44.920 --> 00:05:46.080
Name your price.

00:05:50.420 --> 00:05:51.760
Make sure it's secured!

00:05:51.960 --> 00:05:52.640
Got it.

00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:53.880
Be careful.

00:05:53.920 --> 00:05:54.400
Sure.

00:05:54.640 --> 00:05:55.640
Gao Xiang.

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:57.110
The mic cord should reach

00:05:57.120 --> 00:05:58.120
every table.

00:05:58.320 --> 00:05:59.520
No worries. I'm a pro.

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:02.120
Kinda nervous.

00:06:03.080 --> 00:06:04.080
Wanzhi.

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:06.910
He's on gear, tracks,

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:07.600
and sound.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:08.600
Nice!

00:06:08.760 --> 00:06:09.760
How much?

00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:11.080
No payment.

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:12.240
Yet he wants a cut.

00:06:12.600 --> 00:06:13.600
How much?

00:06:14.520 --> 00:06:16.160
He wanted 40%.

00:06:16.400 --> 00:06:17.800
I talked him down to a third.

00:06:19.520 --> 00:06:20.120
I'm gonna

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:21.120
give him my share.

00:06:21.240 --> 00:06:22.360
Won't bother you.

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:23.840
So you work for free?

00:06:23.960 --> 00:06:24.880
No way.

00:06:24.920 --> 00:06:25.280
Right.

00:06:25.280 --> 00:06:26.000
It's fine.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:26.680
You two

00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:27.800
are teaching me a lot.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:29.000
It's settled then.

00:06:29.120 --> 00:06:30.800
Well, that's a big cut.

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:33.000
But we have no costs now.

00:06:33.280 --> 00:06:34.600
All revenue is profit.

00:06:34.960 --> 00:06:35.960
Still worth it.

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:38.160
Fang Wanzhi!

00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:39.400
Okay now?

00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:40.120
Good.

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:41.310
If you took a smaller cut,

00:06:41.320 --> 00:06:42.320
it'd be even better.

00:06:42.640 --> 00:06:43.640
Out of the question.

00:06:43.880 --> 00:06:44.880
She promised me.

00:06:44.960 --> 00:06:46.000
In partnership,

00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:47.320
a deal is a deal.

00:06:47.880 --> 00:06:48.880
Mr. Gao!

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:49.640
Got the permit.

00:06:49.640 --> 00:06:50.640
Then later...

00:06:50.760 --> 00:06:51.440
Thank you.

00:06:51.480 --> 00:06:51.960
Anytime.

00:06:52.440 --> 00:06:52.880
Dress nice.

00:06:52.880 --> 00:06:53.440
Fang Wanzhi!

00:06:53.720 --> 00:06:55.040
This counts as a cost too.

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:56.280
Processing fee, 30 RMB.

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:58.110
What cost?

00:06:58.120 --> 00:06:58.960
Not even started yet.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.000
See for yourself.

00:07:01.600 --> 00:07:03.600
Temporary Performance Permit?

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.520
It's against regulations

00:07:05.720 --> 00:07:06.760
to charge money

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:08.040
like you did yesterday.

00:07:09.400 --> 00:07:10.640
Didn't even think of that.

00:07:11.720 --> 00:07:12.720
Thanks.

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:14.720
Partnership also means

00:07:14.840 --> 00:07:15.960
everyone pulls their weight.

00:07:16.680 --> 00:07:18.320
I won't mess up tonight.

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:20.160
The rest is in your hands.

00:07:22.920 --> 00:07:23.920
Coming!

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:26.800
May I take your order?

00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:28.360
Sure.

00:07:28.560 --> 00:07:29.560
No problem.

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:31.800
Coming!

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.200
Anything else?

00:07:39.180 --> 00:07:40.540
Sir, which song would you like?

00:07:41.220 --> 00:07:41.620
Choose one

00:07:41.620 --> 00:07:42.200
Sailor.

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:43.480
Sure thing.

00:07:43.960 --> 00:07:44.960
Enjoy!

00:07:45.720 --> 00:07:47.920
Good evening, everyone!

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:51.600
I'm Qian.

00:07:54.640 --> 00:07:55.950
The guest at Table 5

00:07:55.960 --> 00:07:57.840
requested Rose, Rose, I Love You.

00:07:57.880 --> 00:07:59.440
Let's give a round of applause!

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:01.280
Good!

00:08:02.600 --> 00:08:05.320
I'm no pro, but here we go.

00:08:07.640 --> 00:08:12.560
♪ Rose, rose, I love you
with an aching heart ♪

00:08:13.080 --> 00:08:17.880
♪ What is your future?
Now we have to part... ♪

00:08:18.320 --> 00:08:19.440
See anything you like?

00:08:19.520 --> 00:08:20.200
Sailor.

00:08:20.200 --> 00:08:20.640
Sailor?

00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:21.720
Okay.

00:08:21.760 --> 00:08:22.480
Quickly, please.

00:08:22.760 --> 00:08:23.560
Sure thing.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:25.000
Sir, which song?

00:08:25.240 --> 00:08:26.240
This is the list.

00:08:26.320 --> 00:08:26.880
The Choice.

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.040
The Choice?

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.080
Got it.

00:08:29.760 --> 00:08:30.760
This one.

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:32.640
Their order.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:35.560
Thank you.

00:08:35.920 --> 00:08:38.400
Cheers!

00:08:38.840 --> 00:08:45.800
♪ My home's on the Loess Plateau ♪

00:08:46.280 --> 00:08:51.480
♪ Winds sweep down the slopes ♪

00:08:52.160 --> 00:08:54.920
♪ Be it northwest wind ♪

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:58.160
♪ or southeast wind ♪

00:08:58.400 --> 00:09:01.400
♪ They all become my song ♪

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:04.560
♪ My song ♪

00:09:05.200 --> 00:09:06.200
Hey, girl!

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:07.560
Come here.

00:09:07.880 --> 00:09:08.880
Coming.

00:09:09.640 --> 00:09:10.640
What song would you like?

00:09:12.080 --> 00:09:13.520
How Are You, My Friend?

00:09:13.800 --> 00:09:14.280
Okay.

00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:15.560
You sing it.

00:09:15.760 --> 00:09:16.760
I can't.

00:09:17.320 --> 00:09:18.560
Pick another then.

00:09:18.880 --> 00:09:19.880
Anything you know.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.080
Sorry, sir.

00:09:21.080 --> 00:09:22.400
I can't sing.

00:09:22.640 --> 00:09:24.080
You have a beautiful voice.

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:25.800
How could you not sing?

00:09:26.120 --> 00:09:27.120
Don't fool me.

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:28.720
I really can't.

00:09:30.560 --> 00:09:31.560
Can you recite?

00:09:31.760 --> 00:09:32.880
I like your voice.

00:09:33.680 --> 00:09:34.200
I...

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:35.480
Well...

00:09:35.640 --> 00:09:36.640
Embarrassing me, huh?

00:09:37.520 --> 00:09:38.520
I'm out.

00:09:38.560 --> 00:09:39.240
Bye.

00:09:39.560 --> 00:09:40.560
Sir!

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.000
Just as you said.

00:09:42.280 --> 00:09:43.280
I'll recite.

00:09:44.800 --> 00:09:45.800
Take it.

00:09:46.240 --> 00:09:46.720
Okay.

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:47.800
Drink up!

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:49.120
Come on!

00:09:49.280 --> 00:09:50.280
Hello, everyone.

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:52.280
This drink is on us.

00:09:53.480 --> 00:09:54.040
Fang Wanzhi.

00:09:54.280 --> 00:09:55.360
Lots of customers tonight.

00:09:55.480 --> 00:09:56.630
They're

00:09:56.640 --> 00:09:57.320
my target.

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:58.600
Can you fit in

00:09:58.640 --> 00:09:59.720
a quick ad?

00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:00.960
An ad?

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:02.720
Just read the brochure.

00:10:03.200 --> 00:10:04.000
No way.

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:04.840
We finally

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:05.920
created this vibe.

00:10:06.160 --> 00:10:07.000
Oh, please!

00:10:07.080 --> 00:10:08.080
This is a rare chance.

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:09.720
Just an ad.

00:10:14.480 --> 00:10:15.760
The guests at Table 11

00:10:15.840 --> 00:10:17.040
want me to sing.

00:10:17.640 --> 00:10:19.160
But I'm sorry I can't sing.

00:10:19.560 --> 00:10:20.760
I was planning

00:10:20.800 --> 00:10:22.240
to recite the lyrics.

00:10:22.920 --> 00:10:24.600
However, I don't know

00:10:24.640 --> 00:10:25.640
all the words.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:27.360
So I'll improvise a bit

00:10:28.120 --> 00:10:29.840
for them.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:31.160
And for everyone

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:32.400
here tonight.

00:10:32.600 --> 00:10:34.040
Good!

00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:38.840
Every day,

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:40.640
you walk the path

00:10:40.720 --> 00:10:42.440
others have laid out for you.

00:10:43.080 --> 00:10:44.960
One day, you get lost

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:46.480
and leave home.

00:10:46.840 --> 00:10:47.840
That's when

00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:49.920
you find your dream.

00:10:50.400 --> 00:10:53.040
You are willing to pay any price for it.

00:10:54.560 --> 00:10:56.480
No matter how long the journey,

00:10:56.680 --> 00:10:59.200
I'll be by your side.

00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:01.400
Let me show you a path of my own.

00:11:01.720 --> 00:11:04.760
Because of you, I never
stop moving forward.

00:11:06.520 --> 00:11:08.680
How are you feeling now?

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:11.120
Is there still a smile upon your face?

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:14.400
Do you still get little in return?

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:17.680
Do you still give so much?

00:11:18.560 --> 00:11:20.760
May happiness surround you.

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:22.760
Your happiness

00:11:23.160 --> 00:11:24.880
is all I wish for.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:26.080
Good!

00:11:26.600 --> 00:11:28.440
So great!

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:30.040
My friend,

00:11:30.680 --> 00:11:32.080
how are you doing?

00:11:32.440 --> 00:11:33.520
Wishing you peace.

00:11:33.920 --> 00:11:36.480
May nothing stand in your way.

00:11:37.000 --> 00:11:38.000
My friend,

00:11:38.280 --> 00:11:39.600
how are you doing?

00:11:40.680 --> 00:11:41.960
On this beautiful night,

00:11:42.680 --> 00:11:44.080
do you miss home?

00:11:44.760 --> 00:11:46.240
Do you miss your dear mom?

00:11:46.760 --> 00:11:48.800
She worries if you've had enough to eat,

00:11:49.080 --> 00:11:51.840
and hopes that you'll be her pride.

00:11:52.200 --> 00:11:52.920
Wonderful!

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:53.920
Cheers to you!

00:11:57.880 --> 00:11:58.880
This city is big.

00:11:59.680 --> 00:12:01.600
Big enough for everyone's dreams.

00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:03.280
It's also small.

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:04.960
Small enough

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:06.840
to just give you a boost

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:08.160
and help you soar.

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:10.760
Let me introduce someone.

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:12.680
His name is Gao Xiang.

00:12:13.640 --> 00:12:14.640
He set up

00:12:14.640 --> 00:12:15.720
our speakers for free

00:12:16.020 --> 00:12:17.980
and volunteers to perform with us.

00:12:18.360 --> 00:12:19.360
Please welcome him.

00:12:19.880 --> 00:12:22.320
Put your hands together!

00:12:22.340 --> 00:12:23.710
Applause, everyone!

00:12:23.720 --> 00:12:25.120
- Let's thank him!
- Welcome!

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:26.680
What?

00:12:26.940 --> 00:12:28.070
Come on. Get on stage.

00:12:28.080 --> 00:12:28.640
Hurry up.

00:12:28.840 --> 00:12:29.840
Go!

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:32.080
Well... hi, everyone.

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:34.750
He's a teacher at Academy

00:12:34.760 --> 00:12:35.760
of Continuing Education.

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:37.270
It's a place

00:12:37.280 --> 00:12:38.520
for working people to learn.

00:12:38.920 --> 00:12:39.680
It lets you

00:12:39.720 --> 00:12:41.400
chase your dreams

00:12:41.640 --> 00:12:43.960
while working for a living.

00:12:44.680 --> 00:12:45.360
My friend,

00:12:45.640 --> 00:12:46.920
how are you doing?

00:12:47.480 --> 00:12:48.840
On this beautiful night,

00:12:49.160 --> 00:12:50.160
please don't forget

00:12:50.200 --> 00:12:52.040
to miss your mom.

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:53.080
She worries

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:54.640
if you've had enough to eat,

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:56.000
and hopes

00:12:56.240 --> 00:12:58.320
that you'll be her pride.

00:12:58.680 --> 00:12:59.880
Remember his name.

00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:01.240
Gao Xiang.

00:13:01.600 --> 00:13:03.080
Take his business card.

00:13:03.280 --> 00:13:04.800
You will become the person

00:13:04.880 --> 00:13:06.200
your mom always wanted you to be.

00:13:06.520 --> 00:13:07.640
Nice!

00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:09.390
Gao Xiang, give me one!

00:13:09.400 --> 00:13:10.520
Gao Xiang, I need one!

00:13:11.200 --> 00:13:12.400
No problem.

00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:14.880
Here.

00:13:18.360 --> 00:13:18.760
Next,

00:13:18.760 --> 00:13:20.350
these two lovely ladies

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:21.630
will keep singing for us.

00:13:21.640 --> 00:13:23.840
Woohoo!

00:13:25.560 --> 00:13:26.670
Fang Wanzhi,

00:13:26.680 --> 00:13:27.990
you're amazing.

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:29.000
I really admire you.

00:13:29.880 --> 00:13:30.800
If I could sing

00:13:30.800 --> 00:13:31.400
like you,

00:13:31.480 --> 00:13:33.240
I wouldn't be going through this.

00:13:33.280 --> 00:13:34.280
A moment.

00:13:49.800 --> 00:13:52.520
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

00:13:53.120 --> 00:13:53.600
Fang Wanzhi!

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:53.920
♪ I... ♪

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:55.200
Fang Wanzhi!

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:56.840
Hold on!

00:13:57.080 --> 00:13:58.080
Um,

00:13:58.160 --> 00:13:58.960
the boss asked

00:13:58.960 --> 00:13:59.920
if you could start

00:13:59.960 --> 00:14:00.960
two hours earlier.

00:14:03.480 --> 00:14:04.480
Sure!

00:14:04.600 --> 00:14:06.640
He's cashing in, huh?

00:14:06.800 --> 00:14:07.240
Yes.

00:14:07.480 --> 00:14:08.240
We made a lot more

00:14:08.280 --> 00:14:09.320
than usual today.

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:10.840
Your ad is working well too.

00:14:11.000 --> 00:14:11.800
But I'm not doing it

00:14:11.800 --> 00:14:12.320
for free.

00:14:12.360 --> 00:14:13.360
I never said yes.

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:15.030
You didn't say anything.

00:14:15.040 --> 00:14:15.600
That's a yes.

00:14:15.840 --> 00:14:16.560
Yeah,

00:14:16.560 --> 00:14:17.320
you said it!

00:14:17.480 --> 00:14:19.240
In partnership, a deal is a deal.

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:21.790
I only keep the promises I make.

00:14:21.800 --> 00:14:23.440
Not the ones she makes for me.

00:14:23.840 --> 00:14:25.280
What a high-maintenance man.

00:14:25.520 --> 00:14:26.560
Business is business.

00:14:26.720 --> 00:14:27.840
That's the principle.

00:14:28.280 --> 00:14:29.630
Table 11

00:14:29.640 --> 00:14:30.920
made me perform today.

00:14:31.240 --> 00:14:32.760
It was not all about promoting you.

00:14:32.920 --> 00:14:34.440
I'm not keeping score.

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:36.600
Partnerships are just about profit.

00:14:36.760 --> 00:14:37.760
I got that.

00:14:37.920 --> 00:14:38.920
Let's go.

00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:41.440
Two hours earlier tomorrow!

00:14:41.480 --> 00:14:42.480
4:30 PM!

00:14:42.840 --> 00:14:43.880
You agreed!

00:14:52.040 --> 00:14:53.040
Fang,

00:14:53.480 --> 00:14:54.040
what's up?

00:14:54.280 --> 00:14:54.840
Zhu,

00:14:55.160 --> 00:14:56.440
I made some pear soup.

00:14:56.760 --> 00:14:58.160
Was gonna bring it to your dad.

00:14:58.280 --> 00:14:59.280
Perfect timing.

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.320
You take it.

00:15:00.680 --> 00:15:01.760
Thanks so much.

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:05.000
Where were you yesterday?

00:15:05.400 --> 00:15:06.400
Why did you miss dinner?

00:15:06.760 --> 00:15:08.000
Finally had a day off.

00:15:08.360 --> 00:15:09.960
Didn't wanna bother you to cook.

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:11.240
We ate out.

00:15:12.240 --> 00:15:13.880
Eating out costs money.

00:15:14.160 --> 00:15:15.680
We've got our own kitchen.

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:19.080
Come tonight.

00:15:19.600 --> 00:15:20.600
I'll cook you some beef.

00:15:21.320 --> 00:15:22.320
No thanks.

00:15:23.760 --> 00:15:24.960
You should take a break.

00:15:25.440 --> 00:15:26.480
The night view is great.

00:15:26.640 --> 00:15:27.760
You can show Liu around.

00:15:28.560 --> 00:15:29.840
The soup's there. Take him some.

00:15:46.960 --> 00:15:47.960
Wanzhi,

00:15:48.440 --> 00:15:49.800
you're so nice.

00:15:50.200 --> 00:15:51.200
Soothe your throats.

00:15:51.480 --> 00:15:53.200
You need to sing two extra hours tonight.

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:54.400
That's tiring.

00:15:54.800 --> 00:15:55.480
The youngest one

00:15:55.480 --> 00:15:56.960
is taking care of us.

00:15:57.240 --> 00:15:58.560
Well, my work is easy.

00:15:58.760 --> 00:16:00.040
Hard work's on you two.

00:16:01.360 --> 00:16:02.440
Back home,

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:04.240
we would say Gao Xiang has got

00:16:04.840 --> 00:16:05.840
no manners.

00:16:07.360 --> 00:16:08.360
What do you mean?

00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:09.560
A grown man

00:16:09.640 --> 00:16:10.400
pursued women

00:16:10.520 --> 00:16:11.760
just to argue over money.

00:16:12.040 --> 00:16:13.160
How stingy.

00:16:13.680 --> 00:16:15.560
Whether a man's generous

00:16:15.640 --> 00:16:17.760
depends on how much he likes you.

00:16:18.440 --> 00:16:19.760
I thought he was pursuing you.

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:21.640
I was wrong.

00:16:22.480 --> 00:16:23.720
Gao Xiang

00:16:23.880 --> 00:16:24.880
is not bad-looking.

00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:25.960
And he's sharp.

00:16:26.080 --> 00:16:27.080
Not like Liu Zhu.

00:16:27.160 --> 00:16:28.600
Clumsy and dull.

00:16:29.800 --> 00:16:31.120
What are you mumbling about?

00:16:31.920 --> 00:16:32.440
No one

00:16:32.440 --> 00:16:34.240
has chased me in ages.

00:16:34.280 --> 00:16:34.840
Last night,

00:16:34.880 --> 00:16:36.280
many guys drank with me,

00:16:36.360 --> 00:16:36.880
but not one

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:38.080
asked for my number.

00:16:38.280 --> 00:16:39.400
Shenzhen

00:16:39.680 --> 00:16:41.720
is blocking my love life.

00:16:44.800 --> 00:16:47.160
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

00:16:48.400 --> 00:16:51.360
♪ I seriously live every minute ♪

00:16:52.320 --> 00:16:54.880
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

00:16:55.560 --> 00:16:59.480
♪ My heart is beating with hope ♪

00:17:00.000 --> 00:17:02.880
♪ My future is not a dream ♪

00:17:03.200 --> 00:17:04.200
Okay. The Choice.

00:17:04.200 --> 00:17:06.230
♪ I seriously live every minute ♪

00:17:06.240 --> 00:17:07.590
Lady, take a look.

00:17:07.600 --> 00:17:08.960
What song would you like?

00:17:10.880 --> 00:17:13.840
♪ My heart is beating with hope ♪

00:17:14.560 --> 00:17:18.720
♪ Beating with hope ♪

00:17:31.120 --> 00:17:32.240
Qian, how do I look?

00:17:33.080 --> 00:17:34.200
So pretty.

00:17:36.200 --> 00:17:37.840
Today's the last day of the holiday.

00:17:37.960 --> 00:17:38.960
We must give it our all.

00:17:39.160 --> 00:17:39.600
Yeah!

00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:40.360
Sir,

00:17:40.360 --> 00:17:41.560
what would you like?

00:17:43.720 --> 00:17:44.720
Sure.

00:17:47.720 --> 00:17:48.720
Sir.

00:17:50.800 --> 00:17:52.160
No problem.

00:17:52.280 --> 00:17:53.280
Wanzhi!

00:17:53.400 --> 00:17:54.400
Wanzhi!

00:17:55.760 --> 00:17:56.320
Alright.

00:17:56.440 --> 00:17:57.680
Next time.

00:17:58.400 --> 00:17:59.400
Come.

00:18:00.520 --> 00:18:01.630
See that guy

00:18:01.640 --> 00:18:02.640
sitting over there.

00:18:03.520 --> 00:18:04.920
He's been here for three days,

00:18:05.240 --> 00:18:06.720
just staring at you.

00:18:07.480 --> 00:18:08.480
I noticed it.

00:18:08.760 --> 00:18:09.800
Be more careful.

00:18:11.880 --> 00:18:12.880
No worries.

00:18:21.240 --> 00:18:22.240
Song request!

00:18:23.840 --> 00:18:25.440
Good working with you!

00:18:30.920 --> 00:18:31.560
You keep eating.

00:18:31.600 --> 00:18:32.280
I'll put it away.

00:18:32.440 --> 00:18:33.440
Okay.

00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:45.000
Song request.

00:18:45.480 --> 00:18:46.000
Sir,

00:18:46.280 --> 00:18:47.000
time's up.

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:48.000
We're done singing.

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:49.640
The money's yours.

00:18:50.640 --> 00:18:51.640
You sing.

00:18:52.760 --> 00:18:53.800
Well, sir,

00:18:54.040 --> 00:18:55.120
I recognize you.

00:18:55.200 --> 00:18:56.590
You've come every day,

00:18:56.600 --> 00:18:57.040
right?

00:18:57.280 --> 00:18:58.040
Let me tell you.

00:18:58.200 --> 00:18:59.840
Wanzhi can't sing.

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:01.480
How about I sing for you?

00:19:01.680 --> 00:19:03.000
A duet works too.
(Support Admin Watch on kissasia.cam or kisskh.org)

00:19:03.240 --> 00:19:04.240
I'll sing

00:19:04.320 --> 00:19:05.600
whatever you want.

00:19:07.160 --> 00:19:08.160
You sing!

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:09.400
I said, you sing!

00:19:10.720 --> 00:19:11.080
Wait...

00:19:11.080 --> 00:19:11.320
What?

00:19:11.320 --> 00:19:12.320
You... why...

00:19:14.160 --> 00:19:15.160
Nobody move!

00:19:15.800 --> 00:19:16.800
Stay back!

00:19:16.920 --> 00:19:17.920
Back off!

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:21.240
I want you to sing.

00:19:22.640 --> 00:19:24.640
I'm tone-deaf. Really bad.

00:19:26.920 --> 00:19:28.040
She's tone-deaf too.

00:19:30.800 --> 00:19:31.800
Sounds bad too.

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:36.040
But I love it.

00:19:37.120 --> 00:19:38.520
Who are you talking about?

00:19:43.280 --> 00:19:44.320
She sang for you?

00:19:45.760 --> 00:19:46.760
What song?

00:19:48.480 --> 00:19:49.520
Tell Me Please.

00:19:50.120 --> 00:19:50.480
Alright,

00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:52.000
Tell Me Please.

00:19:52.560 --> 00:19:53.560
I'll sing it for you.

00:20:01.240 --> 00:20:04.360
♪ Tell me please ♪

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:08.600
♪ How you so easily ♪

00:20:09.200 --> 00:20:14.080
♪ Smile back at me like an angel ♪

00:20:14.640 --> 00:20:15.640
♪ Can... ♪

00:20:17.040 --> 00:20:17.440
Sir,

00:20:17.480 --> 00:20:18.840
I really can't sing.

00:20:19.480 --> 00:20:20.880
How about we have a drink?

00:20:23.040 --> 00:20:24.040
Cross-cupped.

00:20:24.280 --> 00:20:25.280
Hey...

00:20:26.240 --> 00:20:27.720
She had cross-cupped wine with you?

00:20:28.840 --> 00:20:29.840
Fine.

00:20:30.040 --> 00:20:31.040
Cross-cupped.

00:20:55.080 --> 00:20:55.560
Wanzhi,

00:20:56.000 --> 00:20:57.000
let's go.

00:21:00.960 --> 00:21:02.200
What's wrong, sir?

00:21:03.640 --> 00:21:04.640
Girl,

00:21:07.080 --> 00:21:09.000
she's my first love.

00:21:11.320 --> 00:21:12.320
Really?

00:21:14.680 --> 00:21:16.200
I was poor.

00:21:17.680 --> 00:21:18.840
Couldn't pay the bride price.

00:21:19.520 --> 00:21:20.560
We made a deal.

00:21:21.120 --> 00:21:22.360
I'd work in Shenzhen,

00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:23.720
and she'd wait.

00:21:24.480 --> 00:21:26.240
I worked my ass off.

00:21:28.840 --> 00:21:29.840
Three years.

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:33.240
Three years' sweat for the bride price.

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:35.920
When I got back,

00:21:39.080 --> 00:21:40.760
she already had two kids.

00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:48.720
Sir,

00:21:49.200 --> 00:21:50.200
see the bright side.

00:21:51.520 --> 00:21:52.520
You're hardworking.

00:21:52.720 --> 00:21:53.960
You'll definitely get

00:21:54.000 --> 00:21:55.000
a better girl.

00:21:58.720 --> 00:22:00.040
Life's been hard on me.

00:22:01.720 --> 00:22:02.720
Too hard.

00:22:09.640 --> 00:22:10.640
Sir.

00:22:23.880 --> 00:22:25.120
Life's been hard on me too.

00:23:17.120 --> 00:23:18.120
Girl,

00:23:20.280 --> 00:23:21.280
thanks.

00:23:22.360 --> 00:23:23.360
I'm drunk.

00:23:24.120 --> 00:23:25.360
I came here eight years ago.

00:23:25.960 --> 00:23:26.960
I'm an old-timer now.

00:23:32.680 --> 00:23:33.680
Take this.

00:23:35.600 --> 00:23:36.600
If need help,

00:23:38.080 --> 00:23:39.080
find me.

00:23:44.720 --> 00:23:45.720
Sorry.

00:23:57.320 --> 00:23:58.720
You were too bold!

00:23:58.760 --> 00:24:00.080
You even hugged a stranger!

00:24:00.320 --> 00:24:01.320
That's just a hug.

00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:02.640
It's polite.

00:24:02.960 --> 00:24:04.040
Come on!

00:24:04.160 --> 00:24:05.520
Sounds like you're tough.

00:24:05.760 --> 00:24:07.200
You're the tough one.

00:24:07.360 --> 00:24:08.400
Still sound great

00:24:08.440 --> 00:24:09.640
after three straight nights.

00:24:10.000 --> 00:24:11.520
As great as you?

00:24:11.760 --> 00:24:13.960
You're making fun of me, Hao Qianqian!

00:24:14.920 --> 00:24:15.760
She's mocking me!

00:24:15.800 --> 00:24:16.800
You do sound good.

00:24:17.080 --> 00:24:18.520
You're mocking me too!

00:24:22.480 --> 00:24:24.030
Keep it safe.

00:24:24.040 --> 00:24:25.040
Of course.

00:24:27.400 --> 00:24:28.400
Fang Wanzhi!

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:30.960
Fang Wanzhi!

00:24:35.840 --> 00:24:37.280
I already gave you your cut.

00:24:37.360 --> 00:24:38.400
What now?

00:24:40.320 --> 00:24:41.720
Can we talk alone?

00:24:42.760 --> 00:24:43.760
What's there to say?

00:24:45.280 --> 00:24:46.280
Just hear him out.

00:24:47.600 --> 00:24:48.600
No.

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:49.960
Thanks.

00:24:50.320 --> 00:24:51.320
Hey...

00:24:51.800 --> 00:24:52.440
You talk.

00:24:52.760 --> 00:24:54.000
Real good friends.

00:24:57.240 --> 00:24:58.720
You've got a problem with me?

00:25:00.360 --> 00:25:01.360
Get to the point.

00:25:03.000 --> 00:25:04.000
Here you are.

00:25:04.120 --> 00:25:05.120
This is yours.

00:25:05.600 --> 00:25:06.200
Isn't this

00:25:06.280 --> 00:25:07.280
your cut?

00:25:07.600 --> 00:25:08.600
Why give it to me?

00:25:09.040 --> 00:25:09.720
These days,

00:25:09.960 --> 00:25:10.400
we're

00:25:10.440 --> 00:25:11.560
flooded with applicants.

00:25:11.800 --> 00:25:12.910
I've completed my mission.

00:25:12.920 --> 00:25:14.240
And that's mostly thanks to you.

00:25:14.800 --> 00:25:16.120
Just a token of thanks.

00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:17.840
Business is business.

00:25:20.080 --> 00:25:21.320
Well,

00:25:21.560 --> 00:25:22.640
I provided the gear

00:25:22.680 --> 00:25:23.560
and did the work,

00:25:23.680 --> 00:25:25.310
but I also finished

00:25:25.320 --> 00:25:26.320
a three-month task.

00:25:26.480 --> 00:25:27.520
I'm already rolling in it.

00:25:27.880 --> 00:25:28.880
But you?

00:25:28.920 --> 00:25:29.680
You got nothing

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:30.760
in return.

00:25:30.840 --> 00:25:31.840
That's not fair.

00:25:32.920 --> 00:25:34.320
Hao Qianqian told me.

00:25:34.440 --> 00:25:35.720
You three agreed

00:25:35.760 --> 00:25:36.760
to split it three ways.

00:25:37.000 --> 00:25:37.560
However,

00:25:37.840 --> 00:25:38.960
I butted in.

00:25:39.240 --> 00:25:40.640
And I took your share.

00:25:43.040 --> 00:25:44.200
Don't overlook

00:25:44.320 --> 00:25:45.680
your partner's take.

00:25:45.800 --> 00:25:47.360
That's also a principle of partnership.

00:25:49.240 --> 00:25:50.240
Gotta go.

00:25:51.040 --> 00:25:52.040
By the way,

00:25:54.160 --> 00:25:55.160
your hug

00:25:56.480 --> 00:25:57.480
was amazing.

00:25:58.000 --> 00:25:59.320
I don't believe

00:25:59.360 --> 00:26:00.360
you got expelled.

00:26:00.720 --> 00:26:02.120
Why you left school doesn't matter.

00:26:02.800 --> 00:26:03.800
You weren't the one

00:26:04.640 --> 00:26:05.640
who lost.

00:26:06.680 --> 00:26:07.680
It was school.

00:26:10.200 --> 00:26:11.200
Bye.

00:26:25.840 --> 00:26:27.440
Gao Xiang was stingy.

00:26:27.480 --> 00:26:28.400
Always calculating.

00:26:28.440 --> 00:26:29.080
Never thought

00:26:29.080 --> 00:26:30.640
he would do something this amazing.

00:26:31.040 --> 00:26:32.280
Really that amazing?

00:26:33.280 --> 00:26:35.800
I told you he wanted to chase you.

00:26:36.320 --> 00:26:37.320
See?

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:39.840
He's so into you.

00:26:40.120 --> 00:26:42.120
Into me? No way.

00:26:42.760 --> 00:26:43.360
Chase me?

00:26:43.400 --> 00:26:44.960
He just wants me to sign up.

00:26:45.400 --> 00:26:46.400
Wanzhi,

00:26:46.640 --> 00:26:47.640
count the money.

00:26:47.640 --> 00:26:48.880
What if he pocketed some?

00:26:50.800 --> 00:26:51.800
You count it.

00:26:52.200 --> 00:26:53.200
Okay.

00:27:01.760 --> 00:27:02.240
It's right.

00:27:02.720 --> 00:27:03.720
710.

00:27:03.960 --> 00:27:04.960
For three days.

00:27:05.400 --> 00:27:06.160
Every one of us

00:27:06.160 --> 00:27:07.920
made 710 RMB!

00:27:08.200 --> 00:27:09.400
We should celebrate!

00:27:09.800 --> 00:27:10.520
Exactly!

00:27:10.520 --> 00:27:11.520
Hold on.

00:27:12.840 --> 00:27:14.600
The boss came to me.

00:27:16.720 --> 00:27:17.880
He said

00:27:17.920 --> 00:27:18.920
business is booming

00:27:20.080 --> 00:27:21.800
because of us.

00:27:22.040 --> 00:27:22.600
So,

00:27:23.000 --> 00:27:24.910
we all

00:27:24.920 --> 00:27:27.000
got 200 extra!

00:27:27.120 --> 00:27:28.270
Really?

00:27:28.280 --> 00:27:29.080
Oh my god!

00:27:29.080 --> 00:27:30.800
He's generous!

00:27:31.200 --> 00:27:32.320
How old is he?

00:27:32.480 --> 00:27:33.880
Does he have a son?

00:27:33.920 --> 00:27:35.200
Hao Qianqian!

00:27:37.200 --> 00:27:38.200
Just three days.

00:27:39.080 --> 00:27:40.320
We got 910!

00:27:41.280 --> 00:27:42.280
So great!

00:27:42.720 --> 00:27:43.680
Cheers!

00:27:43.680 --> 00:27:44.800
One more thing.

00:27:45.640 --> 00:27:47.000
Thanks to Qian,

00:27:47.280 --> 00:27:48.520
we made money

00:27:48.720 --> 00:27:49.920
and grew from it.

00:27:50.360 --> 00:27:51.240
I'm telling you.

00:27:51.280 --> 00:27:52.960
I feel so confident now.

00:27:53.320 --> 00:27:54.320
It's not hard

00:27:54.600 --> 00:27:56.160
to make money in Shenzhen.

00:27:56.560 --> 00:27:58.070
Princess of Yu County?

00:27:58.080 --> 00:27:59.080
So what?

00:27:59.080 --> 00:28:01.550
I'm gonna be a Shenzhen star!

00:28:01.560 --> 00:28:02.240
What spirit!

00:28:02.240 --> 00:28:03.000
Cheers!

00:28:03.080 --> 00:28:04.080
Cheers!

00:28:09.600 --> 00:28:10.600
Zhu!

00:28:16.480 --> 00:28:18.160
Let's go in.

00:28:20.520 --> 00:28:21.520
Liu!

00:28:22.000 --> 00:28:23.160
Liu Zhu!

00:28:24.200 --> 00:28:26.080
Have a drink with us!

00:28:26.720 --> 00:28:27.720
Stop.

00:28:29.600 --> 00:28:30.600
It's late.

00:28:30.800 --> 00:28:33.120
And as women, you're drinking?

00:28:34.000 --> 00:28:35.000
Shameful!

00:28:35.200 --> 00:28:36.720
What's wrong with women drinking?

00:28:36.920 --> 00:28:38.440
Just mind your own son.

00:28:39.760 --> 00:28:41.440
Watch your mouth! That's rude!

00:28:41.800 --> 00:28:42.200
Yes!

00:28:42.360 --> 00:28:43.360
Liu!

00:28:43.600 --> 00:28:44.440
If you don't mind,

00:28:44.520 --> 00:28:46.120
come up and have a drink!

00:28:46.280 --> 00:28:47.240
If we're bothering you,

00:28:47.280 --> 00:28:48.640
then I apologize!

00:28:48.960 --> 00:28:50.080
But tonight,

00:28:50.280 --> 00:28:51.520
we're drinking

00:28:51.920 --> 00:28:53.640
until we can't stand!

00:28:54.000 --> 00:28:55.000
Liu,

00:28:55.040 --> 00:28:56.720
today's the last day of the holiday.

00:28:56.880 --> 00:28:58.360
Tomorrow we return to work.

00:28:58.560 --> 00:28:59.560
You're our boss again.

00:28:59.800 --> 00:29:00.640
So tonight,

00:29:00.640 --> 00:29:02.080
please let us drink, okay?

00:29:02.560 --> 00:29:03.560
Dad,

00:29:03.840 --> 00:29:04.840
just let them drink.

00:29:05.200 --> 00:29:05.760
You sleep.

00:29:06.000 --> 00:29:06.760
I'll join them.

00:29:06.760 --> 00:29:07.760
Stop!

00:29:08.160 --> 00:29:09.160
Why would you join them?

00:29:09.480 --> 00:29:11.200
Didn't you get what Fang meant?

00:29:11.880 --> 00:29:13.080
It's still the holiday.

00:29:13.480 --> 00:29:14.560
I can't control them.

00:29:15.040 --> 00:29:16.320
But I can control you!

00:29:17.040 --> 00:29:18.680
Go to bed. Now!

00:29:19.720 --> 00:29:20.160
Drink.

00:29:20.600 --> 00:29:21.600
Just drink.

00:29:21.680 --> 00:29:22.400
If you're late

00:29:22.440 --> 00:29:23.520
tomorrow,

00:29:24.040 --> 00:29:25.040
pay gets docked.

00:29:25.320 --> 00:29:26.320
Yes!

00:29:27.320 --> 00:29:27.680
Come on.

00:29:27.960 --> 00:29:28.960
Go back!

00:29:31.360 --> 00:29:32.240
You two

00:29:32.280 --> 00:29:33.280
are smart.

00:29:33.360 --> 00:29:34.360
A toast to you.

00:29:34.400 --> 00:29:35.400
To Shenzhen.

00:29:35.600 --> 00:29:36.600
To us.

00:30:17.640 --> 00:30:18.320
What's up?

00:30:18.440 --> 00:30:19.480
Breakfast's over.

00:30:19.920 --> 00:30:21.240
Why did you wake me up?

00:30:21.480 --> 00:30:22.320
We were deliberate.

00:30:22.360 --> 00:30:24.670
You let loose last night.

00:30:24.680 --> 00:30:25.800
Sleep in.

00:30:25.960 --> 00:30:27.560
You can get up at 9:40.

00:30:27.880 --> 00:30:28.360
No.

00:30:28.600 --> 00:30:29.600
I missed breakfast,

00:30:29.640 --> 00:30:30.640
and you covered for me.

00:30:31.080 --> 00:30:32.200
I'll wash the dishes.

00:30:32.840 --> 00:30:33.840
Hey...

00:31:03.440 --> 00:31:04.440
Here.

00:31:05.480 --> 00:31:07.040
It helps with the hangover.

00:31:07.600 --> 00:31:08.600
Thanks.

00:31:12.400 --> 00:31:13.760
How do you know I was drunk?

00:31:16.680 --> 00:31:17.680
I told my dad

00:31:18.120 --> 00:31:19.120
not to dock your pay.

00:31:24.760 --> 00:31:26.000
They really went too far,

00:31:26.400 --> 00:31:27.520
getting you this drunk.

00:31:30.880 --> 00:31:31.880
Nobody pushed me.

00:31:32.200 --> 00:31:33.400
I wanted to drink.

00:31:39.000 --> 00:31:40.760
You're beautiful even when drunk.

00:32:02.400 --> 00:32:03.240
What are you doing?

00:32:03.240 --> 00:32:04.240
Fang,

00:32:04.400 --> 00:32:05.480
I dream of you every night.

00:32:05.520 --> 00:32:06.520
My mind is full of you.

00:32:06.760 --> 00:32:07.640
- Be my girlfriend!
- No!

00:32:07.680 --> 00:32:08.720
Let go!

00:32:08.800 --> 00:32:09.880
I love you!

00:32:10.120 --> 00:32:10.840
- I'm...
- You...

00:32:10.840 --> 00:32:11.840
Zhu!

00:32:12.840 --> 00:32:14.000
- Fang! Fang!
- Go out!

00:32:14.040 --> 00:32:14.680
I love you.

00:32:14.680 --> 00:32:15.680
Stay back!

00:32:16.520 --> 00:32:16.840
No.

00:32:17.000 --> 00:32:17.480
Fang,

00:32:17.720 --> 00:32:18.560
I... I really

00:32:18.560 --> 00:32:19.320
love you.

00:32:19.320 --> 00:32:19.960
Stop saying!

00:32:19.960 --> 00:32:20.960
Put the knife down!

00:32:24.160 --> 00:32:25.160
What's up?

00:32:27.480 --> 00:32:28.480
Dad...

00:32:29.600 --> 00:32:30.600
I...

00:32:33.320 --> 00:32:34.320
Go out.

00:32:34.640 --> 00:32:35.640
Get lost!

00:32:43.360 --> 00:32:44.520
I can't control

00:32:44.760 --> 00:32:45.960
what you young people do,

00:32:46.720 --> 00:32:47.720
and it's none

00:32:48.880 --> 00:32:49.880
of my business.

00:32:50.600 --> 00:32:51.600
But anyway,

00:32:52.120 --> 00:32:53.240
you shouldn't pull a knife.

00:32:54.800 --> 00:32:55.840
I'm Zhu's father.

00:32:56.440 --> 00:32:57.440
If he's done

00:32:57.480 --> 00:32:58.520
something wrong,

00:32:59.560 --> 00:33:00.560
I apologize

00:33:00.880 --> 00:33:01.920
on his behalf.

00:33:10.760 --> 00:33:11.520
Ouch!

00:33:11.760 --> 00:33:12.760
Let go, Li Juan!

00:33:12.800 --> 00:33:13.800
Stop messing around!

00:33:14.000 --> 00:33:15.160
I'm not messing around!

00:33:15.600 --> 00:33:16.480
Wanzhi is my bestie.

00:33:16.480 --> 00:33:17.480
I'm warning you.

00:33:17.760 --> 00:33:18.440
Bully her again,

00:33:18.440 --> 00:33:19.600
and I'll twist your ear off.

00:33:20.880 --> 00:33:22.360
It's about to fall off already!

00:33:22.720 --> 00:33:23.840
I never bullied her.

00:33:24.360 --> 00:33:25.120
I like her.

00:33:25.160 --> 00:33:26.280
I treasure her too much.

00:33:26.520 --> 00:33:27.840
She doesn't need that!

00:33:28.440 --> 00:33:29.520
Did you ask her

00:33:29.560 --> 00:33:30.880
if she likes you?

00:33:31.240 --> 00:33:32.960
She never said she didn't.

00:33:33.720 --> 00:33:34.920
Mind your own business.

00:33:35.360 --> 00:33:36.870
Still talking back?

00:33:36.880 --> 00:33:38.040
I'm telling my dad!

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:38.920
I don't care!

00:33:39.120 --> 00:33:40.120
Li Juan!

00:33:40.400 --> 00:33:41.400
Don't go too far!

00:33:42.320 --> 00:33:43.120
You know,

00:33:43.160 --> 00:33:43.840
my dad hired you

00:33:43.880 --> 00:33:45.000
because of me.

00:33:45.520 --> 00:33:46.760
You never even looked at me.

00:33:47.560 --> 00:33:48.440
Fine by me if you're

00:33:48.480 --> 00:33:49.120
with Mr. Zhou.

00:33:49.320 --> 00:33:51.000
Now I'm into Fang, and you're stopping me!

00:33:53.280 --> 00:33:54.280
Enough.

00:33:54.840 --> 00:33:55.840
Stop crying.

00:33:57.320 --> 00:33:58.680
I'm warning you again.

00:33:59.480 --> 00:34:00.640
Fang Wanzhi is my friend.

00:34:00.840 --> 00:34:02.080
Her business is my business.

00:34:05.000 --> 00:34:06.000
She wanna

00:34:07.080 --> 00:34:08.080
talk to you.

00:34:12.800 --> 00:34:13.800
Really?

00:34:19.360 --> 00:34:20.360
Zhu,

00:34:20.920 --> 00:34:22.120
sorry I pulled that knife.

00:34:22.800 --> 00:34:23.800
I apologize.

00:34:24.480 --> 00:34:25.480
It's fine.

00:34:26.240 --> 00:34:27.960
We're family. No need to apologize.

00:34:29.360 --> 00:34:31.480
To be honest,

00:34:32.120 --> 00:34:33.280
I'm not interested

00:34:33.760 --> 00:34:34.760
in Li Juan

00:34:35.600 --> 00:34:36.600
and Hao Qianqian.

00:34:37.920 --> 00:34:38.960
I'm only into you.

00:34:39.600 --> 00:34:40.600
Liu Zhu.

00:34:40.680 --> 00:34:41.960
The first time we met,

00:34:42.320 --> 00:34:43.960
I was drawn to you.

00:34:44.560 --> 00:34:45.760
My dad noticed.

00:34:45.960 --> 00:34:47.400
Otherwise, even with Mr. Hu's word,

00:34:47.720 --> 00:34:49.040
my dad wouldn't have hired you.

00:34:49.400 --> 00:34:50.320
So, the hiring

00:34:50.360 --> 00:34:52.160
was just to find you a wife?

00:34:53.920 --> 00:34:55.520
Don't let that get out.

00:34:56.480 --> 00:34:57.480
Not good.

00:34:59.000 --> 00:35:00.000
Zhu,

00:35:00.520 --> 00:35:01.440
this is

00:35:01.520 --> 00:35:02.520
my first job.

00:35:02.840 --> 00:35:03.840
Anyway,

00:35:04.160 --> 00:35:04.920
I'm grateful

00:35:04.960 --> 00:35:06.120
to you two

00:35:06.200 --> 00:35:07.200
for hiring me.

00:35:07.560 --> 00:35:08.560
Don't mention it.

00:35:08.760 --> 00:35:09.560
You're our family...

00:35:09.640 --> 00:35:10.640
However,

00:35:10.680 --> 00:35:12.280
I need to be clear with you.

00:35:13.040 --> 00:35:14.160
I'm not interested in dating

00:35:14.200 --> 00:35:15.600
or getting married.

00:35:16.080 --> 00:35:17.320
Got it?

00:35:20.520 --> 00:35:21.520
No.

00:35:22.320 --> 00:35:23.320
My dad

00:35:23.480 --> 00:35:24.560
wants to talk to you.

00:35:26.400 --> 00:35:27.640
Maybe you chat with him?

00:35:41.320 --> 00:35:42.320
Freshly brewed.

00:35:51.640 --> 00:35:53.080
In our village,

00:35:53.560 --> 00:35:54.840
our Lius

00:35:55.160 --> 00:35:58.200
are the cream of the crop.

00:35:58.800 --> 00:36:00.000
Five tiled-roof rooms,

00:36:01.680 --> 00:36:03.480
pigs, cattle,

00:36:03.960 --> 00:36:05.280
and two donkeys.

00:36:05.720 --> 00:36:06.720
Last year,

00:36:07.080 --> 00:36:08.840
we bought a tractor.

00:36:09.400 --> 00:36:11.040
Haven't had a chance to drive it yet.

00:36:12.160 --> 00:36:13.520
This canteen

00:36:13.800 --> 00:36:14.800
is mine

00:36:15.280 --> 00:36:16.440
in name only.

00:36:16.840 --> 00:36:17.840
In fact,

00:36:18.400 --> 00:36:20.160
every penny goes to Zhu.

00:36:21.800 --> 00:36:22.800
Liu,

00:36:23.480 --> 00:36:24.800
I don't want to date.

00:36:25.840 --> 00:36:27.240
Zhu has always

00:36:27.640 --> 00:36:28.800
been with me.

00:36:29.840 --> 00:36:31.600
Never really been out.

00:36:31.920 --> 00:36:33.280
He means no harm,

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:35.360
but he's stingy.

00:36:35.960 --> 00:36:38.120
He's saved every last penny

00:36:38.600 --> 00:36:40.000
he's ever earned.

00:36:40.280 --> 00:36:41.640
It should be

00:36:42.760 --> 00:36:45.240
tens of thousands.

00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:47.680
I don't want to date.

00:36:51.840 --> 00:36:52.960
If you

00:36:53.400 --> 00:36:55.200
marry him,

00:36:56.520 --> 00:36:58.920
you'll manage the family and money.

00:36:59.400 --> 00:37:00.400
I'm getting old.

00:37:01.040 --> 00:37:02.440
Don't want to work anymore.

00:37:03.120 --> 00:37:04.120
I'll return home

00:37:04.560 --> 00:37:05.760
and stay with his mom,

00:37:06.760 --> 00:37:07.960
waiting for

00:37:08.440 --> 00:37:09.760
a grandchild.

00:37:10.160 --> 00:37:11.400
Liu!

00:37:11.680 --> 00:37:13.680
I said I don't wanna date.

00:37:17.760 --> 00:37:18.920
Do you think

00:37:19.400 --> 00:37:21.880
Zhu is not worthy of you?

00:37:25.160 --> 00:37:26.200
You're from

00:37:26.440 --> 00:37:28.280
the mountains, aren't you?

00:37:29.120 --> 00:37:31.280
Though you were a college girl,

00:37:31.920 --> 00:37:34.440
you're not something special.

00:37:38.920 --> 00:37:40.320
I don't think I'm anything special.

00:37:41.400 --> 00:37:43.150
If not being with Liu Zhu

00:37:43.160 --> 00:37:43.880
means I can't

00:37:43.920 --> 00:37:44.960
work here,

00:37:45.360 --> 00:37:46.360
just say it

00:37:46.600 --> 00:37:48.160
and take me to Personnel.

00:37:48.440 --> 00:37:49.440
I'll cooperate.

00:37:54.480 --> 00:37:55.480
Have some fish.

00:38:00.880 --> 00:38:01.880
Potatoes?

00:38:13.760 --> 00:38:14.760
Didn't you say

00:38:14.960 --> 00:38:16.160
she's from the mountains?

00:38:16.400 --> 00:38:18.400
Why is she the mayor's daughter now?

00:38:22.360 --> 00:38:23.880
The mayor is her adoptive father.

00:38:24.120 --> 00:38:25.200
She said so herself.

00:38:25.960 --> 00:38:28.360
Don't you know what an adoptive father is?

00:38:29.160 --> 00:38:29.920
Her mother

00:38:30.080 --> 00:38:31.840
was a principal.

00:38:32.360 --> 00:38:33.560
You think you could marry

00:38:34.200 --> 00:38:35.560
such a high-born woman?

00:38:36.200 --> 00:38:37.120
Who do you think

00:38:37.200 --> 00:38:38.360
you are?

00:38:38.600 --> 00:38:39.640
Come on.

00:38:40.080 --> 00:38:41.400
No one is supporting her.

00:38:41.600 --> 00:38:42.320
Or the mayor

00:38:42.320 --> 00:38:43.440
wouldn't let her work here.

00:38:43.840 --> 00:38:45.920
Anyway, she's out of your league.

00:38:46.960 --> 00:38:47.960
Shame on you.

00:38:48.240 --> 00:38:49.840
And you tried to force her?

00:38:50.200 --> 00:38:51.440
If she presses charges,

00:38:51.600 --> 00:38:53.000
you're going to jail!

00:38:53.920 --> 00:38:54.920
I've never been

00:38:55.160 --> 00:38:56.800
so humiliated!

00:38:57.040 --> 00:38:58.560
I must give you a good lesson!

00:38:58.640 --> 00:38:59.120
Dad!

00:38:59.400 --> 00:38:59.920
Dad!

00:39:00.200 --> 00:39:01.200
Don't run!

00:39:01.240 --> 00:39:02.240
I'll...

00:39:02.720 --> 00:39:03.160
Dad!

00:39:03.280 --> 00:39:04.280
No!

00:39:11.800 --> 00:39:12.800
Hao Qianqian,

00:39:13.560 --> 00:39:14.920
how does Liu know that?

00:39:16.000 --> 00:39:17.400
I told him.

00:39:17.680 --> 00:39:18.480
Or Liu Zhu

00:39:18.480 --> 00:39:19.480
wouldn't give up.

00:39:21.480 --> 00:39:22.560
So nosy.

00:39:22.800 --> 00:39:24.320
You're blaming me?

00:39:24.760 --> 00:39:25.760
What? You regret it?

00:39:26.160 --> 00:39:27.440
Then I'll go tell him

00:39:27.600 --> 00:39:28.600
you like Liu Zhu.

00:39:29.560 --> 00:39:30.120
Hao Qianqian,

00:39:30.480 --> 00:39:30.960
Wanzhi

00:39:30.960 --> 00:39:31.800
told us

00:39:31.800 --> 00:39:32.600
to keep it secret.

00:39:32.600 --> 00:39:33.920
You forgot that?

00:39:34.440 --> 00:39:35.960
Spill it again, and you're done.

00:39:38.000 --> 00:39:39.030
Come on!

00:39:39.040 --> 00:39:40.920
You two are the best friends now?

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:42.440
And wanna kick me out?

00:39:42.720 --> 00:39:43.720
No way.

00:39:52.280 --> 00:39:53.800
Wait for me!

00:39:57.400 --> 00:39:58.640
What's the rush?

00:40:03.240 --> 00:40:04.600
I'll bring you some food.

00:40:08.240 --> 00:40:09.880
What does that mean?

00:40:10.120 --> 00:40:11.040
Liu rearranged it

00:40:11.080 --> 00:40:12.320
to target you.

00:40:13.160 --> 00:40:13.720
Qian and I

00:40:13.920 --> 00:40:15.000
switch off on purchasing.

00:40:15.200 --> 00:40:15.920
And we

00:40:15.920 --> 00:40:17.160
share the cutting.

00:40:17.200 --> 00:40:18.680
The hard work all falls on you!

00:40:19.200 --> 00:40:20.960
It's not targeting me.

00:40:21.280 --> 00:40:22.960
I told him I get carsick.

00:40:23.320 --> 00:40:24.680
And knife work is a skill.

00:40:24.880 --> 00:40:25.640
I can't do it.

00:40:25.840 --> 00:40:27.000
Still not fair.

00:40:27.920 --> 00:40:28.960
I'll talk to Liu.

00:40:29.880 --> 00:40:30.880
Li Juan!

00:40:31.200 --> 00:40:31.720
We barely

00:40:31.760 --> 00:40:32.920
put this behind us.

00:40:34.040 --> 00:40:35.040
Let it go.

00:40:36.240 --> 00:40:37.240
Wanzhi,

00:40:37.840 --> 00:40:38.960
you never

00:40:39.000 --> 00:40:40.000
take things lying down.

00:40:41.440 --> 00:40:42.920
You used that idiom well.

00:40:43.400 --> 00:40:44.560
Talking to you every day.

00:40:44.600 --> 00:40:46.400
I'm just picking it up.

00:40:47.280 --> 00:40:48.600
I'm not taking things lying down.

00:40:49.760 --> 00:40:50.440
This is

00:40:50.440 --> 00:40:51.520
my first job.

00:40:51.840 --> 00:40:53.440
I want to finish it smoothly.

00:40:54.200 --> 00:40:55.200
Well, fine.

00:41:00.600 --> 00:41:01.600
Juan, Wanzhi.

00:41:02.240 --> 00:41:03.080
Come here.

00:41:03.160 --> 00:41:04.480
I want to say something.

00:41:05.720 --> 00:41:06.720
What's it?

00:41:07.400 --> 00:41:08.880
Just come.

00:41:11.040 --> 00:41:13.200
You're such a handful.

00:41:13.320 --> 00:41:14.320
Say it.

00:41:15.160 --> 00:41:16.160
What's up?

00:41:17.360 --> 00:41:18.600
How about

00:41:18.640 --> 00:41:19.640
we resign together?

00:41:21.000 --> 00:41:22.150
We could form

00:41:22.160 --> 00:41:23.200
a singing group.

00:41:23.440 --> 00:41:24.560
I already thought of a name.

00:41:24.800 --> 00:41:25.920
Workers' Friends.

00:41:26.520 --> 00:41:27.920
We could sing at food stalls,

00:41:28.080 --> 00:41:29.310
fancy places,

00:41:29.320 --> 00:41:30.320
or nightclubs.

00:41:30.560 --> 00:41:32.240
We could make more money.

00:41:32.440 --> 00:41:33.720
If we get famous,

00:41:33.960 --> 00:41:34.840
we could be on TV

00:41:34.920 --> 00:41:36.440
and even make an album.

00:41:36.800 --> 00:41:38.400
You're never grounded.

00:41:38.640 --> 00:41:40.000
The canteen is fine.

00:41:40.400 --> 00:41:41.320
If I had to

00:41:41.320 --> 00:41:42.550
dress up to busk

00:41:42.560 --> 00:41:43.360
and Mr. Zhou knew,

00:41:43.360 --> 00:41:44.400
he would be angry.

00:41:44.760 --> 00:41:46.520
Those few days, I was so scared

00:41:46.560 --> 00:41:47.760
I'd run into his comrades.

00:41:48.040 --> 00:41:49.240
No ambition.

00:41:49.920 --> 00:41:51.320
Li Juan, don't think like that.

00:41:51.680 --> 00:41:52.680
Not busking.

00:41:52.720 --> 00:41:53.960
It's artistic performance.

00:41:55.600 --> 00:41:56.360
But, Qian,

00:41:56.560 --> 00:41:58.040
we have a year-end bonus.

00:41:58.360 --> 00:41:59.360
Forgot that?

00:42:01.680 --> 00:42:02.280
Besides,

00:42:02.600 --> 00:42:04.040
if we resigned together,

00:42:04.440 --> 00:42:05.760
the canteen would collapse.

00:42:06.200 --> 00:42:07.360
Liu is a kind man.

00:42:07.600 --> 00:42:08.800
We shouldn't screw him over.

00:42:09.320 --> 00:42:10.120
He's taking revenge.

00:42:10.120 --> 00:42:11.440
And you're defending him?

00:42:11.920 --> 00:42:12.920
It's not revenge.

00:42:13.160 --> 00:42:14.280
He just cares about his son.

00:42:14.680 --> 00:42:15.680
It's normal.

00:42:16.320 --> 00:42:17.720
Wanzhi is broad-minded.

00:42:18.200 --> 00:42:19.200
Not like you.

00:42:20.440 --> 00:42:21.240
Anyway,

00:42:21.240 --> 00:42:22.320
it's a good idea.

00:42:22.720 --> 00:42:24.160
But I can't sing.

00:42:24.600 --> 00:42:26.000
And Li Juan is not a pro.

00:42:26.400 --> 00:42:27.920
We can do it occasionally.

00:42:28.440 --> 00:42:30.200
If we really formed a group,

00:42:30.480 --> 00:42:32.480
it'd be very hard to make it.

00:42:35.000 --> 00:42:36.640
But Liu plans

00:42:36.880 --> 00:42:37.840
to find Liu Zhu a wife

00:42:37.880 --> 00:42:38.920
after the Spring Festival.

00:42:39.160 --> 00:42:39.720
And he

00:42:39.800 --> 00:42:40.920
will not run the canteen.

00:42:41.840 --> 00:42:42.600
Time to think about

00:42:42.680 --> 00:42:43.680
our next step.

00:42:45.680 --> 00:42:46.760
Whatever happens,

00:42:47.120 --> 00:42:47.800
you two have to

00:42:47.880 --> 00:42:48.880
take me with you.

00:42:49.040 --> 00:42:50.240
Don't dump me.

00:42:51.360 --> 00:42:52.360
Fine!

00:42:52.960 --> 00:42:53.400
Pinkies.

00:42:53.760 --> 00:42:54.160
Pinkies.

00:42:54.440 --> 00:42:55.440
Pinkies.